text:
英一くん、翠ちゃん両人へマウンティングする市野崎さん……やはり圧倒的アルファ雄で最高以外の言葉が見つかりません！！！！ 💕
前は市野崎さん、後ろは英一くんにおもちゃで攻められながらスイッチが入る翠ちゃんも最高に可愛いし、それを見て興奮する市野崎さんもやらしすぎます……！
でも、あくまでその姿が好きなだけで己が上だということを示す「俺をオナニーの道具にするな」のセリフで全て持っていかれたので、もう市野崎さんの大勝利でいいです……。
trans:
To Eiichi and Midori, Mr. Ichinosaki's relentless dominance... truly, there are no words to describe her other than the ultimate alpha!!!! 💕
Midori, getting switched on while being toyed with by Eiichi from behind and Mr. Ichinosaki from the front, is unbelievably adorable, and seeing Mr. Ichinosaki get turned on by watching that is just too indecent......!
However, the line "Don't use me as a tool for your masturbation," which he delivers to assert his superiority while loving that sight, completely steals the show. Let's just call this an overwhelming victory for Mr. Ichinosaki.
